OL,3,CPrimrose Hill stabbing witness urged
OL,4,Cto come forward with 'vital' video
OL,6,FA video of a fight in a London park
OL,7,Fwhere a 21-year-old student was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death will be "vital
OL,9,Fevidence", police said as they urged
OL,10,Fthe woman who recorded it to come
OL,11,Fforward.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police have urged a
OL,14,F"key witness", described as a young
OL,15,Fwoman or teenager, to help officers
OL,16,F"piece together the sequence of
OL,17,Fevents" which led to the death of
OL,18,FFinbar Sullivan in Primrose Hill on
OL,19,FTuesday.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@IO]vD@AOUvD@MO]xD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
