FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775909466
OL,3,CPrimrose Hill stabbing witness urged
OL,4,Cto come forward with 'vital' video
OL,6,FThe woman, who the police said has not
OL,7,Fcommitted any crimes, was captured on
OL,8,Ffilm recording the fight, which is
OL,9,Fbelieved to have happened shortly
OL,10,Fbefore the stabbing.
OL,12,FIn the footage, she wore a pink vest,
OL,13,Fblue denim shorts and black trainers.
OL,15,FDetective inspector Andy Griffin, who
OL,16,Fis leading the investigation, said:
OL,17,F"My team continues to pursue several
OL,18,Furgent lines of enquiry to establish
OL,19,Fwhy Fin tragically lost his life.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
