PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775909466
OL,3,CPrimrose Hill stabbing witness urged
OL,4,Cto come forward with 'vital' video
OL,6,F"I believe this woman's account of
OL,7,Fevents, as well as the video she
OL,8,Fcaptured, will provide vital evidence.
OL,10,F"To reiterate, she has not committed
OL,11,Fany offence but we are urging her, or
OL,12,Fanyone who may know her, to come
OL,13,Fforward and assist our investigation.
OL,14,FWe need to speak to her as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@JO]
