OL,3,CPrimrose Hill stabbing witness urged
OL,4,Cto come forward with 'vital' video
OL,6,FMr Sullivan, a filmmaking student, was
OL,7,Fstabbed to death in a fight at the
OL,8,Fview point in Primrose Hill in the
OL,9,Fearly evening on Tuesday.
OL,11,FA second man, believed to be in his
OL,12,F20s, was found nearby in Regent's Park
OL,13,FRoad with knife wounds and taken to
OL,14,Fhospital. Police said his injuries are
OL,15,Fnon-life-threatening and non-life-
OL,16,Fchanging.
OL,18,FMr Sullivan's father, Christopher
OL,19,FSullivan, told the Daily Mail his son
OL,20,Fhad gone to Primrose Hill to use a new
OL,21,Fcamera he had got for his birthday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775909466
OL,3,CPrimrose Hill stabbing witness urged
OL,4,Cto come forward with 'vital' video
OL,6,F"This is the worst tragedy I could
OL,7,Fever imagine," the 65-year-old told
OL,8,Fthe newspaper on Thursday.
OL,10,F"He's my only son... I had him when I
OL,11,Fwas 45. He can never be replaced."
OL,13,FHe added: "I'm so broken-hearted, I
OL,14,Fcan't believe it.
OL,16,F"He was the most beautiful, lovely,
OL,17,Foutgoing, loving boy. He was just a
OL,18,Freally lovely person.
OL,20,F"And why he was targeted, we have no
OL,21,Fidea."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@NO]rD@AOUsD@bO]uD@KOUxD@AOU|D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@FO]
