PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775909466
OL,3,CPrimrose Hill stabbing witness urged
OL,4,Cto come forward with 'vital' video
OL,6,FMr Sullivan said his son had ambitions
OL,7,Fto follow in the footsteps of his
OL,8,Fgrandfather, cameraman Michael
OL,9,FSeresin, who worked on Harry Potter
OL,10,FAnd The Prisoner Of Azkaban and Rambo
OL,11,FIII.
OL,13,F"All I can tell you is he was the
OL,14,Fsubject of an indiscriminate stabbing.
OL,15,FHe was not a gang member," Mr Sullivan
OL,16,Ftold the Daily Mail.
OL,18,F"He was just a little groovy 21-year-
OL,19,Fold who loved movies and making films.
OL,20,FHe didn't drink, he didn't smoke, he
OL,21,Fdidn't go out.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@ZO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775909466
OL,3,CPrimrose Hill stabbing witness urged
OL,4,Cto come forward with 'vital' video
OL,6,F"He'd stay at home editing his films
OL,7,Fsix nights a week. He wanted to follow
OL,8,Fin his (grandfather's footsteps) and
OL,9,Fbe a cameraman.
OL,11,F"He recently did a video for Joseph
OL,12,FCorre, Vivienne Westwood's son.
OL,14,F"We were just about to start a company
OL,15,Ftogether... he was going to do his
OL,16,Fshowreel today with me. And now he's
OL,17,Fdead."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUyD@FO]
